==Arabic==
===Particle===
'''{{ARchar|هَل}}''' (hal)

# initial interrogative particle that indicates a yes-or-no question.

====Translations====
*Chinese: [[嗎]], [[吗]] (ma, final rather than initial)
*[[Hindi]]: [[क्या]] (kyā)
*Japanese: [[か]] (ka, final rather than initial)
*[[Khmer]]: [[េទ]] (final rather than initial)
*Mongolian: [[уу]] (uu), [[үү]] (üü), [[юуу]] (yuu), [[юүү]] (yüü)
*Persian: {{FAchar|[[آیا]]}} (āyā)
*Thai: {{THchar|[[ไหม]]}} (mãi, final rather than initial)
*Urdu: {{URchar|[[کیا]]}} (kyā)

